<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<%- include('../partials/public-head') %>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('../partials/public-header') %>

<main>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="wrap">
      <span class="eyebrow">About Us</span>
      <h1>The story behind <%= settings.business_name || 'Chari Fashion' %></h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="wrap section-pad">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-copy reveal">
          <p class="lead-text"><%= settings.about_text || 'Chari Fashion is a Sri Lankan DTF printing studio.' %></p>
          <p>We started with a simple idea: printing should be sharp, reliable, and easy to order — whether it's one shirt for yourself or a hundred for your team.</p>
          <p>Every order goes through the same DTF process: your design is printed onto film, finished with adhesive powder, then heat-pressed onto the fabric. No shortcuts, no second-rate prints.</p>
          <p>We work directly with customers over WhatsApp from quote to delivery, so you always know where your order stands.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-values reveal">
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="gold-rule"></div>
            <h4>Quality First</h4>
            <p>Every print is checked before it leaves the press.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="gold-rule"></div>
            <h4>Honest Pricing</h4>
            <p>Clear prices, confirmed before printing starts.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="gold-rule"></div>
            <h4>Fast Turnaround</h4>
            <p>Most orders are ready within days, not weeks.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-strip">
    <div class="wrap reveal">
      <h2>Want to work with us?</h2>
      <p>Tell us what you need and we'll take it from there.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('../partials/public-footer') %>
</body>
</html>
